Show HN: Daily-updated playlists of artists playing soon near you
text: I created Upcoming Playlists because I often want to go out to see live music, but don’t recognize many of the artists on the calendar. I found myself manually looking up artists and finding great new music and concerts to go to, so I made Upcoming Playlists to automate that process and share with others.

Tony Stubblebine (Medium CEO), Hire Me.
text:
I'm the guy who created the post asking why Medium failed, it prompted you to respond and I applaud you for responding, but you clearly don't know what's actually wrong. You only need to read 30 more comments underneath your reply to start finding out that the main problems your company has are NOT the main points you made.

I've been a long-time user of Medium, and I've been studying what makes a social blogging platform succeed by interviewing the people who actually use Medium. I have excellent ideas on how to make the company succeed. I know how to fix it.

I'm asking for a shot. I want to see Medium succeed, and I would love to help you see it through.

I'll settle for anything, as long as I can help Medium become the platform it used to be.

I will literally fly to Medium HQ today just to have a shot.
